## Context

- We use Shadcn/UI to style our application.

## Rules

- You must use Shadcn UI for components.
- You must use Tailwind CSS for styling.
- You must install any ShadcnUI missing component with `pnpm dlx shadcn@<version used on package.json> add <component-name>`
